author: isobelojalvo
body: First commit of the RCTUnpacker to be used for 2015 data taking with the Stage-1 upgrade. This is to be used only with the CTP7 DAQ firmware output as it assumes a specific protocol. Notice, there is no check to ensure that the FedID is correct. This implementation of RCT Unpacker has been tested with raw dumps from the CTP7 DAQ buffers.
title: Rct Unpacker
